{
  "_comment": "Reference machine config matching the end-of-Section-16 cell state. Cell unchanged since Section 10. The palletizer carries arm, gripper, pick_station, and the three box-dimension attrs (box_width_mm, box_length_mm, box_height_mm); depends_on lists arm/gripper/pick-station. Section 17 adds the pallet dep + 7 place-side states + safety_height_mm + place_dwell_secs. Replace <NAMESPACE> with your org's namespace before pushing. Used as a fallback in Section 17's Setup-check.",
